headline: ‘It Makes No Sense To Me’: Nvidia’s Jensen Huang Slams Americans Who ‘Vilified Energy,’ Praises Trump for ‘Sticking His Neck Out’
summary: Jensen Huang outlines how energy capacity underpins AI leadership, reframing U.S.–China competition as an infrastructure and industrial challenge.

headline: Nuclear Energy Stocks Rise on Increasing Clean Power Demand
summary: Investors looking to gain exposure to nuclear energy may find attractive opportunities in companies such as NextEra Energy, Vistra and OKLO.
